data.description: ***NEW PRICE***!!! This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath house boasts a spacious 3007 sq ft open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. Situated on a sprawling acre lot surrounded by beautiful wooded trees, this home offers the perfect balance of privacy and tranquility! The expansive primary bath features a large walk-in shower, providing a luxurious spa-like experience. Enjoy the great outdoors from the comfort of your own home with the covered patio, perfect for relaxing or hosting outdoor gatherings! The 3 bay garage includes a workshop area, providing ample space for all your DIY projects.  The eat-in kitchen features an island and breakfast bar, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or preparing delicious meals. *DINING ROOM HAS NEW VINYL PLANK FLOORING*! Refrigerators Remain, making move-in day a breeze.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful house your dream home!  **AC AND ROOF REPLACED WITHIN THE LAST 2 YEARS** SHED 2023-10-15
